{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3139b49bd9","title":"华东野战军应派两个纵队培西逃之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c53475d83b","index":0,"year":1948,"month":12,"day":2,"articleId":"3139b49bd9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9f65b5c7b5","type":"paragraph","text":"华东野战军应派两个纵队培西逃之敌”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"3139b49bd9"},{"id":"8be0dbe189","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年12月2日）菜、陈、张，谭、王巴，并告刘、陈、双数向西逃，你们应以两个纵队侧翼兼程西进，赶至政人先头培住，方能围击，不要单靠尾追","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"3139b49bd9"},{"id":"c2f5851493","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"3139b49bd9"},{"id":"b9a5d2c8b5","type":"paragraph","text":"二日七时[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给华东野战军代司令员兼代最治变员菜裕、参谋长陈士架和到参谋长张震等的电报。[2]课、王，指课震林、王建安，当时分别任华东野战军山东兵团政治委员和副司令员。[3]刘、陈、邓，指刘伯承、陈毅、邓小平，当时分别任中原野战军司","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"3139b49bd9"}],"page":{"id":"b3bdcfa429","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"3139b49bd9","start":319,"end":319}}}},"__N_SSG":true}